title: Week 17 NFL DFS Picks & Advice for packed Sunday slate (Fantasy Football 12/31)
description:
Will Brinson and Frank Stampfl link up to offer DFS advice for Week 17 of the NFL season, breaking down all the options in the final week of the regular season.
Quarterbacks (1:00)
Running Backs (10:15)
Wide Receivers (31:00)
Tight Ends (43:00)
